only just in the US

346
00:18:48,560 --> 00:18:50,200
but it works internationally.

347
00:18:50,195 --> 00:18:52,565
So for example you might
be traveling to some place

348
00:18:52,564 --> 00:18:55,664
like Hong Kong and you might not
know what the emergency number

349
00:18:55,667 --> 00:18:58,507
is to call but your
Apple Watch does.

350
00:18:58,503 --> 00:19:05,743
[ Applause ]

351
00:19:05,743 --> 00:19:08,983
So in this case, it calls
999 rather than 911.

352
00:19:08,980 --> 00:19:11,250
So this is an emergency
feature that isn't one

