"Taking a moment every day

477
00:24:32,036 --> 00:24:34,676
to do some deep breathing
can reduce stress,

478
00:24:34,672 --> 00:24:36,342
calm the body-mind as well

479
00:24:36,340 --> 00:24:38,580
as have a long term
health benefits."

